<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Lỗi 500 - Server Error</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy"
  content="default-src 'self'; img-src 'self' data: blob: https:; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' 'unsafe-eval' https://cdn.tailwindcss.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline'; font-src 'self'; connect-src 'self' http://localhost:5000">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 flex items-center justify-center">
  <div class="max-w-xl w-full bg-white shadow rounded p-6 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-2">500 - Lỗi máy chủ</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Đã xảy ra lỗi trong quá trình xử lý. Vui lòng thử lại sau.</p>
    <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
      <pre class="text-left bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded text-sm overflow-auto"><%= error %></pre>
    <% } %>
    <div class="mt-6">
      <a href="/dashboard" class="px-4 py-2 bg-purple-600 text-white rounded hover:bg-purple-700">Về Dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>


